      "name": "HC Business Approach",
      "settings": {
        "section_anchor_id": "our-approach",
        "business_eyebrow": "Our Business Approach",
        "business_heading": "No Shareholders. \nNo Private Jets.",
        "business_body": "<p>People often ask why big clothing brands don't just do what we do. The honest answer: their incentives won't let them.</p><p>Most large brands answer to shareholders. That means every decision — materials, manufacturing, pricing — gets filtered through one question: what's best for the stock price? Better materials cost more. Higher standards cut into margins. In that system, you're not really the customer. You're a line item with a credit card.</p><p>We decided early on that we didn't want to build that way.</p><p>It wasn't easy. Our founder Wen spent everything he had to buy out our early shareholders — and came dangerously close to losing it all. At some point, faced with the choice between going broke or going hollow, he picked broke. Turns out an empty wallet is easier to live with than an empty conscience.</p><p>So today, HercLeón is fully independent. No shareholders to answer to. No quarterly earnings call to dress up. Just us, our products, and the people who wear them.</p><p>There's an African proverb we keep coming back to: \"If you want to go fast, go alone. If you want to go far, go together.\" We're not trying to be the fastest brand in the room — just the one still standing when it matters. And the only way to do that is to stay honest, stay independent, and occasionally remind ourselves that a great jacket outlasts a great stock tip.</p>",
        "product_image_alt": "Fabric yarns and fibers",
        "product_eyebrow": "Our Product Approach",
        "product_heading": "Engineering first. \nAlways.",
        "product_intro": "<p>We don't design products to follow trends. We design them to solve problems real ones, that real people deal with every day. That means doing the work most brands skip:</p>",
        "product_footer_lead": "If something can be meaningfully improved, we feel responsible for trying.",
        "product_footer_taglines": "Even when it's difficult.\nEven when it's expensive.\nEven when most brands wouldn't bother.",
        "padding_top_mobile": 64,
        "padding_bottom_mobile": 64,
        "padding_top_desktop": 128,
        "padding_bottom_desktop": 128
      }
