      "name": "HC Why This Matters",
      "settings": {
        "section_anchor_id": "our-purpose",
        "eyebrow": "The Impact",
        "heading": "Why this matters",
        "lead": "We didn't set out to build a clothing company. We set out to stop people from missing out on their own lives.",
        "body_paragraph_1": "That's what bad gear actually costs you — not money, but moments. The evening you stayed in. The trip you overpacked for. The morning lost to laundry instead of living.",
        "body_paragraph_2": "HercLeón exists to give that back. Clothes that stay fresh longer mean less water wasted and less gear in landfills. But the real return is personal — the confidence to show up without second-guessing, the freedom to move through life without your closet calling the shots.",
        "closing": "Better design makes better clothes. But more importantly, it makes more room for everything that actually matters.",
        "padding_top_mobile": 64,
